We are bringing back our Chua Thian Poh Distinguished Speaker Series (CTPDSS) in 2019 with Speaker Mr. Eric Swanson, Director of Acacia Communications. 
Mr. Swanson has served in a variety of technical and managerial roles in academic, entrepreneurial, industrial and non-profit organisations. To date, he is a co-founding/founding board member of five start-up companies: Advanced Ophthalmic Devices, Lightlab Imaging, Sycamore Networks, Curata Incorporated and Acacia Communications. 
In Innovation and Entrepreneurship: Personal Observations, hear his take on entrepreneurship and learn from personal lessons he has drawn through his startups. 
Visit our website for more details!
